Documentation on Pillow can be found in the following papers and web
addresses: 


D. Cabeza, M. Hermenegildo. Distributed WWW Programming using
(Ciao-)Prolog and the PiLLoW Library. Theory and Practice of Logic
Programming, Vol. 1, Num. 3, pages 251-282, Cambridge U. Press, May
2001.

Paper online:

http://clip.dia.fi.upm.es/papers/pillow-tplp_bitmap.pdf
http://clip.dia.fi.upm.es/papers/pillow-tplp.ps



D. Cabeza, M. Hermenegildo, S. Varma. The PiLLoW/Ciao Library for
INTERNET/WWW Programming using Computational Logic Systems(also
available in ps). Proceedings of the 1st Workshop on Logic Programming
Tools for INTERNET Applications, pages 72-90, September 1996.

Text and code available from:
http://www.clip.dia.fi.upm.es/miscdocs/pillow/pillow.html. 

Paper online:
http://clip.dia.fi.upm.es/papers/pillow-ws-dist_bitmap.pdf
http://clip.dia.fi.upm.es/papers/pillow-ws-dist.ps
